      <h4>The Artist Hospitality Helper</h4>

      <div class="jumbotron col-md-12 container">
        <h1 class="animated fadeInDown"></h1>
      </div>

      <p>Festival numbers are at an all time high, both in the number of existing festivals as well as in the number of people attending.</p>

      <p>The festival industry has been around for about 60 years, and as a young industry, we haven’t caught up to technology, and it’s about time we do.</p>

      <p><strong>EasyRider</strong> creates a solution to all these problems by providing a software and paired smart phone application. 

It sorts all the items asked for in the many riders received and creates a compiled list.

This list can be filtered by item type, who it’s for, and what stage it goes to, allowing for a one-stop-shop for the artist hospitality team to use.

This makes it easier to shop, distribute, and keep the artists happy!
</p>
